				\begin{document}$$_{2}$$\end{document}) and by 11% in the EU28 (from 4005.45 Gg CO2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
